ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule l.1 to the Financial Administration Act
PrecisAmendment to SCHEDULE I.1 to the FINANCIAL ADMINISTRATION ACT by striking out the reference to the Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development in column II of that Schedule opposite the name of the Office of the Co-ordinator, Status of Women in column I of that Schedule and by substituting for that reference a reference to the Minister of Labour in column II of that Schedule opposite that name, effective July 15, 2013.
